Package: vulkanR
Type: Package
Title: Offscreen GPU Renderer Using Rust and wgpu
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "vulkanR", family = "Developer", email = "developer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides an offscreen GPU renderer for R using Rust, extendr, and wgpu. Features headless rendering to PNG files with WGSL shaders compiled at runtime. Supports Vulkan backend on Windows/Linux and Metal on macOS for deterministic rendering without requiring Vulkan SDK installation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust toolchain with rustc and cargo); GPU with Vulkan (Windows/Linux) or Metal (macOS); on CI: mesa-vulkan-drivers, vulkan-tools, libvulkan1
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    png,
    base64enc,
    rextendr
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.1
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
